Invocation Name: feel better
des:
This skill is a mood booster that helps you get through your day with positive one-liners. Just say 'Alexa, open feel better' to invoke the skill. You can say keep saying next to listen. You can say help at any point or stop to exit.
Feel better instantly with this Alexa skill that gives you the positive energy you need to get through your day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
